  "title": "Project Engineer / Project Manager #79391",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building and Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Project Engineer / Project Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Islandwide (Office at Tuas, Transport provided at Joon Koon MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (8.00am – 5.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee day-to-day site works to meet design, specs, and plans.</li><li>Lead the site team; plan and execute daily activities.</li><li>Manage manpower, materials, and equipment to stay on schedule and within budget.</li><li>Track subcontractor progress and quality; resolve issues promptly.</li><li>Work with main contractor and consultants on design reviews, approvals, and technical queries.</li><li>Attend progress meetings with clients, main con, and consultants; report site status.</li><li>Enforce EHS standards and site housekeeping.</li><li>Deliver the project on time, within budget, and to required quality.</li><li>Other tasks as assigned by Management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Engineering, Construction Management, or related field.</li><li>Minimum 2 years’ project management experience in building/civil works.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79391 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
